Description:
Designer lifestyle living at its best
Striking lines and designer styling define this double story home built last year fashioned to the latest style and of the highest quality.
This high-end 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home comes with grand proportions and an enviable open plan design with all the prestige extras and located right near display homes and opposite to Outlook Park that features multi use courts (basketball & tennis), BBQs, playground and some great artwork.
Cleverly accommodating with master-suites upstairs and down plus 3 living areas & balcony with panoramic views , this streamlined home is prestige appointed with designer tapware, quality tiles in each bathroom , refrigerated cooling & ducted heating system, laminate flooring, alarm for security, a well-positioned powder room, and auto double garage with rear roller door access to homemade gym and patio.
Heart of the home is this modern kitchen well-appointed with 900mm stainless steel appliances, stone bench tops, clear glass splash back, dishwasher, large walk in pantry. Being heart of the home, this gorgeous kitchen is central to everything including dinning/family area as well as large alfresco which then takes you to my favorite the big outdoor entertaining area, that offers prettily designed combination of grass and decked area plus in ground water feature & professionally landscaped gardens.
Close proximity to Selandra Rise & Clyde Shopping Centre, St.Peters College & Wilandra Rise Primary School, medical centres & bus stop offer great convenience.
Evoking luxury and flair, this impressive abode is sure to be taken fast, so contact us today on 0401489262 for viewings.

Description:
Modern Home in Growing Estate
This top quality three bedroom home is sensibly designed to maximise living flexibility whilst also offering a little more space where you need it.
Featuring a large open living area with a well appointed kitchen with good sized island bench and plenty of storage. Quality stainless steel appliances and large pantry. The kitchen looks over the expansive dining and main living room with sliding doors opening to the outdoor entertaining area and rear yard.
A second living room/ rumpus room positioned at the front of the home for your convenience. The master bedroom has a walk-in-robe and ensuite. Remaining bedrooms with carpet and built-in-robes. Full sized family bathroom with skylight and good sized laundry which has plenty of storage.
Ducted reverse cycle air conditioning throughout to keep you and your family the perfect temperature all year round. Double lock up garage with direct house access and rear roller door.
Externally this home has an outdoor entertaining area under roofline for family and friend gatherings. Low maintenance front and rear gardens.
Positioned in a growing estate, near sporting facilities, school and walking tracks. Call today to arrange your inspection!
